rComments: She's really nice and clearly wants everyone to do well. Tests and quizzes are easy; homeworks are incredibly hard, and you should absolutely go to TA sections. She is however really bad at getting grades back-took us 'til week 9 to get our midterms back, and she's consistently late submitting final grades. That's annoying but otherwise, thumbs up.

Professor Zhao was great. She clearly wants her students to pass the class and her exams are clear cut and to the point, easy A if you study the slides.  However, while her lectures were easy to understand, the hw was on a whole other level of awful since it was written by the TAs but she was very nice during office hours when asked for help.
